Use scissors on any 'soft' item (artificial or natural) to get 25 value. 2. Then, use the frame on that 'cut soft' item to get a 45 value item. I consistently got 45, but never 50. Framing *uncut* 'natural, hard' items yields 20 value, but combining them also ruins the frame. message: Focus on 'artificial' and 'soft' items. Use 'scissors' on two separate 'artificial, soft' ingredients to create two 'cut' items, each worth 25.
